public void addRenaming(String identifier, String oldPath, String newPath) {
    // Check if identifier already exists
    for (DifferenceGroup group : differenceGroups) {
        if (group.getIdentifier().equals(identifier)) {
            // Overwrite old high level change
            group.setRenaming(new Renaming(oldPath, newPath));
            return;
        }
    }

    // Identifier not found, create new difference group
    DifferenceGroup newGroup = new DifferenceGroup(identifier);
    newGroup.setRenaming(new Renaming(oldPath, newPath));
    differenceGroups.add(newGroup);
}
``` 

This code adds a renaming high level change to a list of difference groups. If a difference group with the same identifier already exists, it overwrites the old renaming change. If not, it creates a new difference group with the given identifier and adds the renaming change to it.

